{"tid":57348,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暫為DQ案議員籌得18萬","createTime":"2016-12-28T02:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T08:29:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e72385b4f107baa554ad6f040186576479bceabf","tid":57348,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T02:29:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19878801&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19878801%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161228&d=IJnNHdeO5SHS6%2FwiWg0FZRpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=ef00b68c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19878801%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20161228&h=238e6c8e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19878801&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20161228</a><br />\n<br />\n暫為DQ案議員籌得18萬<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n陳健民<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民陣決定將元旦遊行籌得的捐款捐予由佔中發起人陳健民、朱耀明和民主動力創會召集人鄭宇碩成立的「守護公義基金」，為4名遭政府入稟要求取消立法會議員資格的議員，應付司法覆核官司需要。基金自上周四公佈成立後，至今籌得逾18萬元，與目標500萬元仍有一段距離，陳健民呼籲更多港人捐款。<br />\n<br />\n陳健民籲踴躍捐款<br />\n<br />\n民陣召集人區諾軒昨指，扣除元旦遊行的成本開支後，會將當日籌得款項捐予基金，他指過往民陣發起元旦遊行時，只希望維持收支平衡，沒有積極動員籌款，有時甚至連收支也無法平衡，故難以估計今次籌款數目。<br />\n<br />\n陳健民則指，目前所接觸過的政治團體中，民主黨、工黨、香港眾志和社民連均答應將市民當日捐款捐予基金，公民黨暫未回覆。他坦言，擔心市民因為特首梁振英放棄連任而鬆懈，故此對當日遊行人數及籌款數目「心入面冇底」，只盼市民踴躍參與，堅守公義。漫畫家黃照達則為基金設計標誌，一把傘下寫着「守護公義基金」，代表「香港人攜手為公義遮風擋雨」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張文鈴<br />\n<br />\n上一則:&nbsp;民陣號召萬人元旦遊行<br />\n<br />\n下一則:&nbsp;南港島綫今通車巴士小巴改道配合　西段落成要等到2026年"},{"pid":"4d14774172c996cac8009f5d9c66953ef28dd3fe","tid":57348,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:22:58.000Z","msg":"錢 真係易搵"},{"pid":"010269b8be802b833fb59d490448f14947ce8e0b","tid":57348,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:25:09.000Z","msg":"泛民自己比囉<br />\n今年唔打隨時連扮反對派都唔洗慘過condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dec8af57139b253bfd2c41e3e428d5f5aed5b50","tid":57348,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:30:48.000Z","msg":"竟然有18萬"},{"pid":"7104996cb30b40ad00e0812b4aee50105a532d80","tid":57348,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53d8eea8d8a58e4291dcf08c47329423b9532b1e","tid":57348,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T04:08:12.000Z","msg":"4個咋<br />\n割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果兩個係咪唔當佢係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbaf66ea01fafca5b6e51c0e5057bc50c027bf3","tid":57348,"uid":50018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:03:39.000Z","msg":"梁游都籌到sing 50萬喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92f157fe49fd844067d096b3ddde2795281dc33","tid":57348,"uid":50018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梁游都籌到<span style=\"color: red;\">sing</span> 50萬喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成<br />\n<br />\n廣東話輸入法，sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c1339dc5a183db00adbc8df46ac870c47f431a","tid":57348,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T08:05:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梁游都籌到sing 50萬喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n50萬???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44aa0ecbf02a52308a68fc3fbdc3da81f9d0307c","tid":57348,"uid":50018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201